                            <p class="text-justify">The airline offers you economy class and business class services. The Ethiopian airlines business class is named Cloud Nine. If you travel with the Cloud Nine, you are provided with onboard amenities and a wide variety of reading material, sleeper seats, and on-demand Ethiopian airlines music and video services having 85 channels on 15.4-inch IFE screens. </p>
